                <head>393. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On March 13, Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_BWL1">Beaulac</persName> and
                    Chilean Minister for Foreign Affairs <persName corresp="#p_BBEO1">Enrique O.
                        Barbosa Baeza</persName> signed a new Public Law 480 agreement in <persName
                        corresp="#p_RSI1">Santiago</persName>. The agreement, which entered into
                    force on June 2, provided for the sale of United States agricultural commodities
                    to Chile valued at approximately $34.6 million. For text, see 7 UST 1007.</p>
            </div>
